languages.text: [draft]{g|Encyclopedia:PsykerPowersGlossary}Psychic powers{/g} that target allies have a chance not to {g|Encyclopedia:DamageGlossary}damage{/g} the {g|Encyclopedia:VeilThickness}veil{/g}. The chance is equal to the highest of <u>5×({g|Encyclopedia:WarhammerFellowship}FEL{/g} {g|Encyclopedia:Bonus}bonus{/g})</u>%, and is based on the highest Fellowship among the Psyker and all allies targeted by the psychic power.

traits.locale_text: [draft]Psychic powers that target allies have a chance not to damage the veil. The chance is equal to the highest of <u>5×(FEL bonus)</u>%, and is based on the highest Fellowship among the Psyker and all allies targeted by the psychic power.
